## Stack Conventions

- Runtime: Bun (not Node.js)
- HTTP framework: Elysia
- Database ORM: Prisma
- UI interactivity: htmx (no JavaScript framework)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + daisyUI
- Auth: EasyAuth
